---
title: Beyond Meat® and Apple Burgers with Roasted Potatoes and Mixed Greens Salad
description: Beyond Meat® and apple come together in the form of a juicy burger. Just when you think it can't get any better, we've added roasted potatoes and a leafy side salad as the perfect accompaniments.
